Definition: law) a person who creates a trust by giving real or personal property in trust to a trustee for the benefit of a beneficiary
Example: a person who gives such property is said to settle it on the trustee
Synonyms: noun, group, law, c, trustor, donor, a, person, who, creates, trust, by, giving, real, or, personal, property, in, to, trustee, for, the, benefit, of, beneficiary, gives, such, is, said, settle, it, on
Category: noun.person
